Cc: Sean Christopherson <seanjc@google.com>
Cc: Paolo Bonzini <pbonzini@redhat.com>
Cc: David Woodhouse <dwmw2@infradead.org>

v3:
 - Re-work the juggle_shinfo_state() thread

v2:
 - New in this version.
